<!DOCTYPE html>
<!-- BETLEGEND DAILY SPORT BOARD SKELETON (multi-game, PREVIEW_PAGE_STANDARD.md, locked July 4 2026).
     Replace every {{PLACEHOLDER}}. Head/meta/nav/hero/calendar conventions identical to
     featured-preview.template - abbreviated here; copy the full head from that skeleton with:
       - og:image / twitter:image / NewsArticle image = {{UNIQUE_HERO_IMAGE_URL}} (marquee game
         action photo, HTTP 200 verified, NEVER newlogo.png)
       - schema: NewsArticle + BreadcrumbList (+ SportsEvent for the marquee game)
       - <link rel="stylesheet" href="/preview-article.css"> after the inline style block
       - window.FORCED_PAGE_DATE = post date -->
<html lang="en">
<head>
{{FULL_HEAD_PER_FEATURED_TEMPLATE}}
</head>
<body>
{{FULL_SITE_NAV}}

<header class="hero">
<div class="hero-badge">{{SPORT}} - {{Weekday, Month D}}</div>
<h1>{{STORYLINE HEADLINE FOR THE DAY'S BOARD - names marquee teams/players}}</h1>
<p>{{LEDE - the day's board in one paragraph: game count, marquee matchups, stakes.}}</p>
</header>

<div class="page-wrapper">
<aside class="calendar-sidebar">
<div class="calendar-box">
<div class="calendar-title">{{SPORT}} Archive</div>
<div class="year-display" id="cal-year">{{YYYY}}</div>
<select class="month-select" id="month-select"></select>
<div class="calendar-weekdays"><span>Su</span><span>Mo</span><span>Tu</span><span>We</span><span>Th</span><span>Fr</span><span>Sa</span></div>
<div class="calendar-days" id="calendar-days"></div>
</div>
</aside>
<div class="mobile-archive">
<div class="mobile-archive-title">{{SPORT}} Archive</div>
<select class="mobile-archive-select" id="mobile-archive-select"><option value="">Jump to date...</option></select>
</div>

<main class="main-content">

<figure class="hero-figure">
<img class="feature-photo" src="{{UNIQUE_HERO_IMAGE_URL}}" alt="{{MARQUEE PLAYER/TEAMS + action}}"/>
<figcaption>{{WHAT THE PHOTO SHOWS | Photo: {{SOURCE}}}}</figcaption>
</figure>

<div class="toc-box">
<div class="toc-title">On Today's Board</div>
<ul class="toc-list">
<li><a href="#game-1-{{away}}-{{home}}">{{Away}} vs {{Home}} - {{hook}}</a></li>
<li><a href="#game-2-{{away}}-{{home}}">{{Away}} vs {{Home}} - {{hook}}</a></li>
<!-- one li per game article below -->
</ul>
</div>

<article class="game-preview marquee" id="game-1-{{away}}-{{home}}">
<div class="game-number">Marquee Matchup</div>
<div class="broadcast-badge">{{Local / NATIONAL NETWORK}}</div>
<div class="game-header">
<img alt="{{AWAY_FULL}}" class="team-logo" src="{{AWAY_LOGO}}"/>
<div class="matchup-info">
<h2>{{Away}} vs {{Home}}</h2>
<span class="game-time">{{Weekday}}, {{TIME}} ET | {{VENUE}}, {{CITY}}</span>
</div>
<img alt="{{HOME_FULL}}" class="team-logo" src="{{HOME_LOGO}}"/>
</div>
<div class="preview-content">
<p>{{Para 1 - records, stakes, why this is the marquee. Verified numbers only.}}</p>
<p>{{Para 2 - away side: starter/form/stats.}}</p>
<p>{{Para 3 - home side: starter/form/stats, the matchup read.}}</p>
</div>
</article>
<div class="game-divider"></div>

<article class="game-preview" id="game-2-{{away}}-{{home}}">
<div class="game-number">{{Angle label - e.g. Ace On The Mound}}</div>
<div class="broadcast-badge">{{Local / NETWORK}}</div>
<div class="game-header">
<img alt="{{AWAY_FULL}}" class="team-logo" src="{{AWAY_LOGO}}"/>
<div class="matchup-info">
<h2>{{Away}} vs {{Home}}</h2>
<span class="game-time">{{Weekday}}, {{TIME}} ET | {{VENUE}}, {{CITY}}</span>
</div>
<img alt="{{HOME_FULL}}" class="team-logo" src="{{HOME_LOGO}}"/>
</div>
<div class="preview-content">
<p>{{3 substantial matchup-specific paragraphs, stats woven in. Analysis only, no picks.}}</p>
</div>
</article>
<!-- repeat per game, game-divider between -->

<div class="related-links">
<div class="related-title">More {{SPORT}} On BetLegend</div>
<ul>
<li><a href="{{SPORT_PREVIEW_HUB}}.html">{{SPORT}} Game Previews</a></li>
<li><a href="{{SPORT_ARCHIVE}}.html">{{SPORT}} Preview Archive</a></li>
<li><a href="{{SPORT}}-records.html">{{SPORT}} Verified Records</a></li>
<li><a href="handicapping-hub.html">Today's Handicapping Hub</a></li>
</ul>
</div>

</main>
</div>

<footer>
<p>&copy; {{YYYY}} BetLegend Picks. All Rights Reserved.</p>
<p><a href="privacy.html">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="terms.html">Terms of Service</a> | <a href="contact.html">Contact</a></p>
</footer>
<script src="scripts/{{SPORT_CALENDAR_JS}}?v={{CACHEBUST}}"></script>
</body>
</html>
